BusyUART = returns the UART transmissions status

CloseUART = turns off the UART module

ConfigIntUART = configures the UART interrupts

DataRdyUART = returns the UART receive buffer status

OpenUART = configures the UART module

ReadUART = returns the content of UART receive buffer

WriteUART = writes data to be transmitted into transmit buffer register

getUART = reads a string of data of specified length and stores it into
	the buffer location specified

putsUART = writes a string of data to be transmitted into the UART transmit buffer

UARTGetErrors = retrieves bitmap of various error values

UARTClearErrors = clears all error flags

EnableIntURX = enables the UART receive interrupt

EnableIntUTX = enables the UART transmit interrupt

DisableIntURX = disables the UART receive interrupt

DisableIntUTX = disables the UART transmit interrupt

SetPriorityIntU = sets priority for UART channel

SetSubPriorityInt = sets the sub priority for UART channel

UARTSendBreak = initiates break sequence on UART

UARTEnableAutoAddr = enables the automatic address matching mode of UART

 

